convert-public-function-to-private - Convert public functions to private

USAGE:
    convert-public-function-to-private <function-name>

DESCRIPTION:
    Convert a public function to a private function by
    renaming it with an underscore prefix.

ARGUMENTS:
    function-name
        Name of the public function to convert (required)

EXAMPLES:
    convert-public-function-to-private my_function
